{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Set in the 1980s, you take on the role of a private detective, tasked with solving cases where justice has faltered. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863340/extras/3254100_901.jpg?t=1733818667\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Each case will challenge you to navigate intricate crime scenes, question witnesses, and gather evidence with your keen deductive skills. You can revisit crime scenes at different times of day, catching suspects off guard and unraveling the hidden truths within their stories. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Murder Avenue</strong> is a demanding detective game for fans of true crime and mystery, emphasizing sharp observation, critical thinking, and the exhilarating pursuit of justice in a world where it doesn\u2019t always prevail. <br> <br><strong>You're a real detective.</strong> <br>Step into the shoes of an investigator. Study the cases. Examine crime scenes, using your keen instincts to uncover hidden clues. Question witnesses and interrogate suspects. Your choices will determine whether the culprit ends up behind bars or slips away. <br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863340/extras/3254100_897.jpg?t=1733818667\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The detective's office is your second home.</strong><br>There's always a hefty stack of case files waiting on your desk, each one demanding your full attention. And don't forget to crack the window open\u2014too much cigarette smoke can cloud your judgment.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863340/extras/3254100_896.jpg?t=1733818667\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2863340/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733818667","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps